---
import BentoCard from '@/components/ui/BentoCard.astro'
---

<BentoCard class="group p-8 col-span-3 md:col-span-2 group" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:flex-row lg:gap-12 pt-4 h-full">
    <!-- Text Content Left (Desktop) / Top (Mobile) -->
    <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center text-center md:items-start md:text-left z-10">
      <h2
        class="font-heavy text-4xl font-bold text-brand md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl mb-2 uppercase leading-[42px]! text-shadow-title text-center! md:text-left!"
      >
        Las 24 <span class="text-4xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">chocolatinas</span>
      </h2>
      <p
        class="font-century text-xl text-white/90 md:text-2xl max-w-md text-balance mb-8 mx-0 md:mx-auto lg:mx-0"
      >
        Únicas e irrepetibles
      </p>

      <!-- Desktop List -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex flex-col space-y-8 mt-8 w-full">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2 group">
          <p
            class="font-century text-white text-lg max-w-xs group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300 text-balance text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs leading-snug"
          >
            <span class="text-brand pr-1 text-sm -mt-1">◆</span> Diseñadas para que recordemos los mejores
            momentos de Ibai
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2 group">
          <p
            class="font-century text-white text-lg max-w-xs group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300 text-balance text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs leading-snug"
          >
            <span class="text-brand pr-2 text-sm -mt-1">◆</span>Ediciones exclusivas que solo
            probarás 1 vez
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2 group">
          <p
            class="font-century text-white text-lg max-w-xs group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300 text-balance text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs leading-snug"
          >
            <span class="text-brand pr-1 -mt-1 text-sm">◆</span> Algunos placeres, los verdaderamente
            especiales, existen precisamente por eso: porque no duran para siempre
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Chocolates + Sabor -->
    <div class="flex flex-2 flex-col items-center w-full z-10">
      <!-- Floating Chocolates Row -->
      <div
        class="relative w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-12 perspective-1000 mb-10 md:my-0 min-h-[150px] md:min-h-[330px]"
      >
        <!-- Chocolate A Group -->
        <div class="relative z-20 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            src="/chocolate_a.webp"
            alt="Chocolatina Big Ibai diseño A"
            class="w-64 md:w-96 lg:w-[16rem] object-contain drop-shadow-2xl floating-chocolate-a group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:rotate-6"
          />
          <p
            class="font-handwriting text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white/90 text-center transform -rotate-6 text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs leading-none"
            style="font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive;"
          >
            El calcetín de <br />
            <span class="text-brand">YouTube</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Chocolate B Group -->
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            src="/chocolate_b.webp"
            alt="Chocolatina Big Ibai diseño B"
            class="w-64 md:w-96 lg:w-[16rem] object-contain drop-shadow-2xl floating-chocolate-b group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:-rotate-6"
          />
          <p
            class="font-handwriting text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white/90 text-center transform rotate-6 text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs leading-none"
            style="font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive;"
          >
            El cinturón de <br />
            <span class="text-brand">La Velada</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative Elements -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen animate-pulse pointer-events-none"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Desktop Sabor Box (Horizontal) -->
      <div
        class="hidden md:flex flex-row items-start gap-4 xl:gap-8 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 xl:p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/20 w-full max-w-4xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 mt-4"
      >
        <h4 class="font-heavy text-xl xl:text-3xl text-brand shrink-0">SABOR</h4>
        <p class="font-century text-white/80 text-sm leading-snug text-pretty">
          Bajo una cobertura suave de chocolate con leche, se esconde un corazón cremoso de relleno
          de leche, pensado para derretirse justo cuando el sabor y la textura alcanzan su punto
          perfecto.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile Description (Sabor) -->
    <div class="md:hidden w-full mt-8 px-4">
      <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/20 w-full">
        <h4 class="font-heavy text-2xl text-brand mb-2 text-center">SABOR</h4>
        <p class="font-century text-white/80 text-lg leading-relaxed text-center text-pretty">
          Bajo una cobertura suave de chocolate con leche, se esconde un corazón cremoso de relleno
          de leche.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile List -->
    <div class="md:hidden w-full mt-8 px-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 group">
        <p
          class="font-century text-white text-lg max-w-xs group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300 text-balance text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs"
        >
          <span class="text-brand pr-1 text-sm -mt-1">◆</span> Diseñadas para que recordemos los mejores
          momentos de Ibai.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 group">
        <p
          class="font-century text-white text-lg max-w-xs group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300 text-balance text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs"
        >
          <span class="text-brand pr-2 text-sm -mt-1">◆</span>Ediciones exclusivas que solo probarás
          1 vez.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 group">
        <p
          class="font-century text-white text-lg max-w-xs group-hover:text-brand transition-colors duration-300 text-pretty text-shadow-black text-shadow-2xs"
        >
          <span class="text-brand pr-1 -mt-1 text-sm">◆</span> Algunos placeres, los verdaderamente especiales,
          existen precisamente por eso: porque no duran para siempre.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BentoCard>

<style>
  .perspective-1000 {
    perspective: 1000px;
  }

  @keyframes float-a {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: rotate(-10deg) translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: rotate(-5deg) translateY(-20px);
    }
  }

  @keyframes float-b {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: rotate(10deg) translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: rotate(15deg) translateY(25px);
    }
  }

  .floating-chocolate-a {
    animation: float-a 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .floating-chocolate-b {
    animation: float-b 7s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }
</style>
